products.title: Genesis White Roller Blind
products.description: A stunning accent for any interior style, this delightful white blind will refresh your space with its tranquil white colourway. Dress any window with the genesis white roller blind and whether it is in a bathroom, hallway or kitchen, the simple style will enhance the sense of openness in the room whilst offering the privacy you need. Product id: sdb-rbx1781 fabric colour: white material: 100% polyester headrail: durable aluminium roller tube supported by white steel brackets - top, face or side fix control type: smooth continuous-looped chain energy saving rating: er2 - medium energy saving value - effective thermal retention light filtering: yes genesis white roller blind in white.
